window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>He can save the world if he doesn’t lose his mind.</b></p> <p>Neuromuscular degeneration. That’s the scientific term for when a psionic Elite begins to go insane.</p> <p>Ward Moreno thought he was immune, but now he’s losing his memories. While he knows the loyal women at his side will never leave him, he can’t protect them if he can’t function.</p> <p>As the vengeful shaman Malagath continues to take revenge on all humanity, Ward’s only chance is to travel to ancient monastery deep in Galatea. There he’ll either find a cure...or lose his mind forever.</p>"; 
